snippet.textDisplay:
It is the people that have the least that are the nicest most giving, genuine people. They are the ones that will help others out when they need it the most, because they know what it’s feels like too be in need and to be without. How devastating it feels when you have nothing and nobody will help.
It is the people who have a lot that NEVER help, because They have never been in a situation were they were really down and out!
I believe everyone should go through a hard time in their life, it causes them to have real compassion for others.
It helps them too understand what is truly important in life. That the most expensive cars, designer clothes, and top brands are not important, it is the ones you love, your family, the people that you hold dear too you that should mean the most.
Things can be replaced, money is worth nothing if you have no one to share it with!
